Changelog:
0.2.0 Alpha II
-Features: 
	Load online ArchWiki article from offline page via top of page link or menu button, improved page formating, removed find-in-page feature
-Performance: 
	layouts now use dp, removed background color main layout
-Stability: 
	uses-sdk merged, debuggable option remove, DefaulActivity now abstract class, AsynTasks cancel on destroy, new check for loaded pages before formatting
-Refactors: 
	new intent .DISPLAY_WIKI_PAGE, new application ArchWikiOfflineApplication, new activity DefaultListActivity modified about text,
	created error message and toast, created arrarys.xml

0.1.4
-API minimum level lowered to 7 (Android 2.1)
-Improved Stability;)
-Removed "index" from topics list

0.1.3
-New placeholder artwork
-Menu: Implemented Home, Find in Page. Search and About menu items
-Add explicit support for large screens for Kindle Fire (and others)
...


